;;    `query-replace-read-args' - 1. Uses `completing-read' if
;;                                   `replace-w-completion-flag' is
;;                                   non-nil.
;;                                2. Default regexps are obtained via
;;                                   `search/replace-default'.
;;                                3. Deactivates region if
